This package contains original package code and bundled tokenizer assets under a
mixed-license distribution.

Bundled tokenizer asset origins:
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M2 tokenizer.json: upstream modified MIT license with a
  "MiniMax M2" UI attribution condition.
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-M1-40k tokenizer.json: Apache License 2.0.
- MiniMaxAI/MiniMax-Text-01-hf tokenizer.json: the upstream repository ships
  both LICENSE-CODE (MIT) and LICENSE-MODEL (MiniMax Model License); review
  both texts below and the accompanying NOTICE file.

Supported aliases such as MiniMax-M2.1, MiniMax-M2.5, MiniMax-M1-80k,
MiniMax-M1-40k-hf, MiniMax-M1-80k-hf, and MiniMax-Text-01 are mapped to the
bundled canonical snapshots above and are not shipped as separate tokenizer
assets in this package.

You must comply with the terms that apply to the bundled asset you redistribute.

